# Master ignore file for Atomberg Goal Portal

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/
package-lock.json

# Environment Secrets (Crucial to prevent AD credential leaks!)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Build Outputs
**/.next/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# IDE / System Logs
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
.vscode/
.idea/
